# Projects gallery

## Content schema (keep stable)

Frontmatter fields: `title`, `summary` (‚â§15 words), `date` / `dateEnd` (optional ISO dates), `label`, `image` (optional local), `href` / `hrefLabel` (optional), `order`.

- Timeline uses `YYYY` | `YYYY-MM` | `YYYY-MM-DD` strings in `index.astro`
- Project card dates: store real `Date`s; format via `formatProjectDate` (e.g. same-month range ‚Üí `Apr 10‚Äì12, 2026`)
- Month precision: `YYYY-MM-01`. Year precision: `YYYY-01-01`
- No project detail pages unless asked. Image is not clickable; only the text link is

## Images

- Host locally under `src/assets/projects/` ‚Äî never hotlink LinkedIn/CDN (URLs expire; Astro cannot optimize remotes)
- Keep sources **uncropped**. Card shows full image with `object-fit: contain` over a blurred self-backdrop (tiny second `<Image>` + CSS blur), not a hard crop that cuts faces
- Optimize with `astro:assets` `<Image>`: WebP, quality ~80, lazy, `widths`/`sizes` matching fluid card width
- Missing image ‚Üí SVG placeholder from `project-placeholder.ts` (seeded by id)

## Card UI

- Horizontal single-row scroller, full-bleed past the 38rem column
- Fluid width for **all** viewports ‚Äî shared CSS vars on `.projects`, **no** hard mobile‚Üídesktop breakpoint that swaps formulas
  - `--card-width: min(20rem, 100vw - 2*pad - peek)`
- Label: solid filled accent badge, top-right over media, text uses `--accent-fg` (white/black), not accent-colored text
- Desktop/fine-pointer: prev/next chevron buttons under the scroller (no visible scrollbar); touch keeps swipe + peek
- Order in body: date (if any) ‚Üí title ‚Üí summary ‚Üí link

## Accent (site-wide)

`--accent` / `--accent-fg` on `:root` (orange). Use for project labels, project/nav links, and timeline dots ‚Äî keep one accent system, don‚Äôt invent a second palette per component.
